<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ترتيبها ٢٠ ... سُورَةُ طَهَ ... آياتها ١٣٥ ... مكية<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الآية ... الكلمة ... معناها<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{اسْتَوَى}</span> ... ارْتَفَعَ، وَعَلَا عَلى الْعَرْشِ، اسْتِوَاءً يَلِيقُ بِجَلَالِهِ وَعَظَمَتِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الثَّرَى}</span> ... التُّرَابِ النَّدِيِّ؛<span class="c5"> وَالمُرَادُ:</span> الأَرَضُونَ السَّبْعُ؛ لِأَنَّهَا تَحْتَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{آنَسْتُ}</span> ... أَبْصَرْتُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بِقَبَسٍ}</span> ... بِشُعْلَةٍ تَسْتَدْفِئُونَ بِهَا.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(١٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{هُدًى}</span> ... هَادِيًا يَدُلُّنَا الطَّرِيقَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{الْمُقَدَّسِ}</span> ... المُبَارَكِ المُطَهَّرِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(١٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِذِكْرِي}</span> ... لِتَذْكُرَنِي فِيهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَكَادُ أُخْفِيهَا}</span> ... أَقْرُبُ أَنْ أَسْتُرَهَا مِنْ نَفْسِي.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَتَرْدَى}</span> ... فَتَهْلِكَ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{أَتَوَكَّأُ عَلَيْهَا}</span> ... أَعْتَمِدُ عَلَيْهَا فِي المَشْيِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَهُشُّ بِهَا عَلَى غَنَمِي}</span> ... أَهُزُّ بِهَا الشَّجَرَ؛ لِتَرْعَى غَنَمِي مَا يَتَسَاقَطُ مِنْ وَرَقِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(١٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَآرِبُ}</span> ... مَنَافِعُ، وَحَاجَاتٌ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(٢٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَسْعَى}</span> ... تَمْشِي بِسُرْعَةٍ وَخِفَّةٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سِيرَتَهَا}</span> ... حَالَتَهَا.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{جَنَاحِكَ}</span> ... جَنْبِكَ تَحْتَ العَضُدِ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>